    • Class org.moeaframework.util.progress.ProgressEvent

      class ProgressEvent extends Object implements Serializable
      serialVersionUID:
      -1133068166971961110L

      • Serialized Fields

        • currentAlgorithm
          Algorithm currentAlgorithm
          The current Algorithm being run.
        • currentNFE
          int currentNFE
          The current number of objective function evaluations for the current seed.
        • currentSeed
          int currentSeed
          The current seed being evaluated, starting at 1.
        • elapsedTime
          double elapsedTime
          The elapsed time in seconds.
        • executor
          Executor executor
          The executor from which these progress reports originate.
        • isSeedFinished
          boolean isSeedFinished
          true if this event was created in response to a seed finishing; false otherwise. This indicates that new results are available in the executor.
        • maxNFE
          int maxNFE
          The maximum number of objective function evaluations per seed. If -1, then no maximum NFE is set.
        • maxTime
          double maxTime
          The maximum elapsed time per seed in seconds. If -1, then no maximum time is set.
        • percentComplete
          double percentComplete
          The percent complete as a fraction between 0 and 1.
        • remainingTime
          double remainingTime
          The estimated remaining time in seconds.
        • totalSeeds
          int totalSeeds
          The total number of seeds to be evaluated.
